# TES Runtime Capabilities

This rule is TES-owned runtime capability, not project-owned governance. It may
be refreshed by the deterministic installer while `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`,
`CURSOR.md`, and previous project-owned Cursor rules are recovered from `.tes/bk/**`.

## TES Command Intents

